# TsekTxt Test Cases — Coverage & Status Report

Comparison of the 79 test cases in [TsekTxt Test Cases.csv](file:///home/dogecheemss/Repos/taglish-credibility-checker/automation/TsekTxt%20Test%20Cases.csv) against our Selenium automation suite ([run_selenium_tests.py](file:///home/dogecheemss/Repos/taglish-credibility-checker/automation/run_selenium_tests.py)).

**Latest run**: 2026-07-13 17:12 — **35 executed, 34 passed, 1 warning, 0 failed**

---

## Legend

| Symbol | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| ✅ Done | Has actual result from automation — mark **Status = Done** in CSV |
| 🔧 Automatable | Could be added to Selenium script |
| 🚫 Not Automatable | Requires manual testing, external load tools, or physical devices |

